d to the presentation of translation volumes and language channels, as raised by Mr. Damien Kurek. Minister Morneau emphasized their commitment to making the CERB available for people in need, considering challenges faced by various groups, and reviewing eligibility criteria for programs like the Canada emergency business account to ensure broader coverage. This proactive approach demonstrates the government's dedication to addressing issues and concerns raised by opposition members to better support vulnerable Canadians during the pandemic.">
